library(arules)

##     abbreviate, write
data <- read.csv(file = "AppleStoreClean.csv", head = TRUE)
tdata <- read.transactions("AppleStoreClean.csv", quote="", sep=",")
## Warning in asMethod(object): removing duplicated items in transactions

HCLUST

distance = dist(as.matrix(data), method = "euclidean")
## Warning in dist(as.matrix(data), method = "euclidean"): NAs introduced by
## coercion
# perform clustering
hc = hclust(distance)

# cut the tree
clusterCut <- cutree(hc, 300)

# plot dendrogram
plot(clusterCut)
